<section xml:id="zbarcode.installation" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
 &reftitle.install;

 <para>
  Use <option role="configure">--with-zbarcode[=DIR]</option> when compiling PHP. The DIR is an 
  optional parameter to ZBar library installation.
 </para>

 <para>
  Use <option role="configure">--with-zbarcode-imagemagick-dir[=DIR]</option> 
  to specify location of the ImageMagick library.
 </para>

</section>


